==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Smattering
<hw>Smat"ter*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A slight, superficial
knowledge of something; sciolism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I had a great desire, not able to attain to a superficial skill in
any, to have some <qex>smattering</qex> in all.</q>
<rj><qau>Burton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Smear</ent>⟦br⟧
